title: Champion Men's Double Dry Moisture Wicking Ankle Socks; 6, 8, 12 Packs Available
description: MULTI PACK – Stock up with a convenient socks value pack – because you don’t ever want to run out.
CHAMPION STYLE – These cushioned socks feature knit-in C logos for pure Champion sports style.
WICKS SWEAT – Double Dry technology in these moisture wicking socks controls sweat buildup so feet stay cooler and drier.
ARCH SUPPORT – You can depend on a secure, stable fit thanks to dedicated arch support.
CUSHIONED BOTTOM – Half-cushioned foot bottom serves as a shock absorber for high-impact comfort.
RIBBED CUFF – Men’s athletic socks feature a low-profile ribbed cuff that hits at the ankle.

Designed to keep you cool and comfortable, Champion® men’s ankle socks help you power through your routine. Double Dry™ technology wicks moisture so you stay cooler and drier no matter how hard you go. A cushioned footbed acts as a shock absorber so your feet are more protected during a high-impact workout. Arch support ensures a comfortable, secure fit. Crafted from a soft, polyester/spandex blend, these men’s athletic socks hug your foot and hit at the ankle. The cherry on top? All pairs of this socks multipack feature the iconic knit-in C logo for a boost of pure Champion style.
